headline: FIS Launches Enhanced Private Capital Suite to Power the Future of Private Equity
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., September 23, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced it has reengineered its Private Capital Suite as a cloud-native software-as-a-service (SaaS) solution. It has also been upgraded into a fully front-to-back solution by integrating FIS' newly launched Investor Services Suite.
